data.description: Come see this beautiful home! True pride of ownership! This home features (3) Bedroom's, which Two are Master Suites! (3) Bathrooms, and an oversized (3) Car Garage! When entering this home, you will notice the beautiful wood flooring, large open floor plan, beautiful cabinetry and fireplace. Large laundry room, with sink, with many custom touches. As you exit through double doors, you will be greeted by so much color with roses, and trees including a covered patio! The (3) Car Garage has very high ceilings that are 8.5 Ft garage doors, lights are on auto timer, and so much more! Buyer & Buyers Agent to verify all information.
